body.p:
If you need to add some of the map metadata to the header of the front page (for example, the
        creation date), add the following CSS rules in your customization
        CSS:*[class ~= "front-page/front-page"] > 
  *[class ~= "map/topicmeta"] > 
    *[class ~= "topic/critdates"] > 
      *[class ~= "topic/created"]{
    string-set: mapcreated attr(date);
}


@page front-page {    	
     @top-center {
          content: "Created: " string(mapcreated);
     }
}The
          front-page is the name of a page that used to present the element with the class
        "front-page/front-page". The above page rule is combined with the default styles.
